title: Wo Shi Jiang Xiaobai 2nd Season (I'm Joybo 2nd Season)
synopsis: After coming to terms with their past, Jiang Xiaobai and Tong Li are still together as editor and authorâ€”and now, as lovers too. But not everything is smooth-sailing for the new couple. Tong Li's most recent work is being panned by readers and critics, and Wen Zheng Magazine's recent decline in sales means that her serialization is in jeopardy.
